<h2 class="bold font-l">Friendship Games</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
After it becomes clear that Crystal Prep's Principal Abacus Cinch went too far with manipulating Twilight Sparkle into participating the titular event, including releasing the stolen Equestrian magic which nearly led to the destruction of both Equestria and their world, everyone from Canterlot High and Crystal Prep begin to turn against her, prompting Cinch to calmly leave. </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
